{"tid":940134,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好迷茫，有無巴打入黎比d意見","createTime":"2018-12-13T16:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T00:14:13.000Z","uid":76601,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"563ff0cffad0429ad1f21baa22acb7ad998aeab2","tid":940134,"uid":76601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"諗左好耐出唔出post,<br />\n我就黎結婚，<br />\n我同拍左4年拖既女朋友自宣布結婚後，我個細佬同佢拍左10年拖既女朋友不停做小動作，網上post野中傷我地，我同我女朋友都好唔開心。<br />\n講過比好多朋友知，亦都講過比父母知，因為以上野都係細佬女朋友係主謀，所近最後父母唔比佢黎我地婚禮。<br />\n但其實細佬因爲佢女朋友無得黎婚禮更加深深不忿，加上我同我女朋友都有條刺。<br />\n到過大禮果日， 細佬全日黑口黑面， 我同我女朋友都好燃嬲。覺得男家果邊無理過我地感受，係都要拉埋細佬同我地。<br />\n佢而家好想唔搞聯婚，但其實我想聯婚，唔聯婚我可以同女朋友結婚，但變相同屋企簽衰仔紙，但調轉就婚都結唔到仲要分手， 麻煩客位巴仔屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9013e3430564ac83103c2eface0bd43defb731","tid":940134,"uid":76601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512ea85613d09fbb45737b31c278c38b478927f9","tid":940134,"uid":62294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪得我睇唔明"},{"pid":"df3e01ec71c258baa568c452368c664e88d55619","tid":940134,"uid":76601,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"512ea85613d09fbb45737b31c278c38b478927f9","tid":940134,"uid":62294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪得我睇唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"麻煩睇多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929a80bb1f5b921ecb5ff6e2c66c585fb1011185","tid":940134,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2